  We have identified some issues leading to your suspended license that may be eligible under this program for assistance. Due to the large number of records we are reviewing it could take up to 12 months for your cases to be reviewed. To protect your privacy, please enter your email address below and we will send you an update when your case has been reviewed. Please allow up to 12 months. You will get an automatic update as soon as we know more about your case. If you have any upcoming or pending traffic court case, you should go to court on your court dates.
</p>

<%= form_for Contact.new do |f| %>
  <%= hidden_field_tag :ids, nil, value: params[:ids] %>

  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="form-group">
      <%= f.label :method, "Contact Method:" %>
      <%= f.select :method, options_for_select(['Email', 'Text message'], 'Email'), class: 'form-control' %>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <%= f.text_field :info, placeholder: 'Contact information', class: 'form-control'%>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= submit_tag 'Save', class:'btn btn-primary' %>
<% end %>

